      "value": {
        "latex": "Effectuer la division suivant les puissances croissantes {\\`a} un ordre $n$\n    quelconque de $1$ par $(1-X)^2$.",
        "html": "<p>Effectuer la division suivant les puissances croissantes\n<span>à</span> un ordre <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span>\nquelconque de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(1\\)</span> par <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\((1-X)^2\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7f0e1ec9-0974-4da9-bca4-27467a0d9e04",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$1 = (1-X)^2 (1 + 2X + 3X^2 + \\dots + nX^{n-1}) + (n+1)X^n - nX^{n+1}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(1 = (1-X)^2 (1 + 2X + 3X^2 + \\dots +\nnX^{n-1}) + (n+1)X^n - nX^{n+1}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "36cfa0c3-2280-497f-81d4-ab24cd5d0391",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En d{\\'e}duire $1 + 2\\cos\\theta + 3\\cos2\\theta + \\dots + n\\cos (n-1)\\theta$,\n    $n \\in \\N^*$, $\\theta \\in \\R$.",
        "html": "<p>En d<span>é</span>duire <span class=\"math inline\">\\(1 + 2\\cos\\theta +\n3\\cos2\\theta + \\dots + n\\cos (n-1)\\theta\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(n \\in \\N^*\\)</span>, <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\theta \\in \\R\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e63b8aa8-20a3-4186-aa6c-0fe7dacb99b2",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$=\\frac {-n\\cos n\\theta + (n+1)\\cos (n-1)\\theta -\\cos\\theta}\n                      {4\\sin^2{\\textstyle{\\frac\\theta2}}}.$",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(=\\frac {-n\\cos n\\theta + (n+1)\\cos\n(n-1)\\theta -\\cos\\theta}\n                      {4\\sin^2{\\textstyle{\\frac\\theta2}}}.\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    }
